{"article_id":"fVowIrh58guFQABz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Senate impeachment trial resumes Monday at 11 a.m. EST .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Refresh this page for updates .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"House impeachment managers and President Donald Trump 's legal team will make their closing arguments Monday","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"as senators prepare to vote on whether to convict or acquit the president on charges of abuse of power and obstruction of Congress .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Those two articles of impeachment were approved by the Democratic-controlled House on Dec. 18 after a two-month inquiry into allegations","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that Trump held up military aid","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to pressure Ukraine into announcing investigations for his political benefit","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"- including one","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"involving former Vice President Joe Biden , a Democratic rival in the 2020 election .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"Trump has insisted","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"he did nothing wrong","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"and was acting to combat corruption .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"His defense team has said","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"the House failed to prove its case ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"that the abuse of power charge is too subjective","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"and the obstruction of Congress charge robs the president of his right","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"to claim executive privilege in court .","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"Attorney Alan Dershowitz made the argument ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"which many legal scholars dispute ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"even if the allegations were true ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"they were n't impeachable","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"because they did not constitute a crime .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"Last week , the Senate voted 51-49 against issuing subpoenas for additional witnesses and documents ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"which would have delayed the trial 's conclusion .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Each side will have two hours to argue the case a final time","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"before senators take to the floor","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to deliver speeches","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"explaining how they view the charges .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"With a 53-47 seat Republican majority in the Senate and a two-thirds vote","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"needed for conviction ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"it is almost certain the president will be acquitted in the final vote on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"What we know :","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"Senators will vote Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"to acquit or convict Trump Impeachment and 2020 election :","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Warren , Sanders , Klobuchar and Bennet will have to juggle Trump impeachment trial and the Iowa caucuses Monday","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"The lead House impeachment manager , Rep. Adam Schiff , D-Calf. , said Sunday","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Democrats `` proved the corrupt scheme","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that they charged in the articles of impeachment . ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"`` That 's pretty remarkable","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"when you now have senators on both sides of the aisle admitting","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"the House made its case","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"and the only question is :","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"'Should the president be removed from office","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"because he 's been found guilty of these offenses ? ' ''","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"Schiff said on CBS News","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"' `` Face the Nation . ''","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Schiff said","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"even if the Senate votes to acquit ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"`` it 's enormously important that the president was impeached ''","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"because","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` by standing up to this president","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"as we have ,","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"by making the case to the American people ,","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"by exposing his wrongdoing ,","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"we are helping to slow the momentum away from our democratic values . '' `","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"` But I 'm not letting the senators off the hook .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"We 're still going to go into the Senate this week","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"and make the case","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"why this president needs to be removed , ''","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"`` It will be up to the senators to make that final judgment","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and the senators will be held accountable for it . ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Schiff declined to say","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"if the House would continue to seek testimony from former national security adviser John Bolton ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"who says in his upcoming book","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"that Trump told him","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"the aid to Ukraine was tied to the investigations","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"Trump desired ,","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"according to news media reports .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"But he said","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"one way or the other , `` the truth will come out . ''","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"'We want to hear that ' :","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"News of John Bolton 's book casts shadow over Trump impeachment trial","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"GOP Sens . Joni Ernst of Iowa and Lamar Alexander of Tennessee said Sunday","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"while Trump 's acts were not impeachable ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"he should have gone through the Department of Justice","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"if he had concerns about Biden and his son 's former position on the board of Burisma , a Ukrainian energy company .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` I think ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"generally speaking , going after corruption would be the right thing","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"to do , ''","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Ernst ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"who declared","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"she will vote to acquit ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"said on CNN 's `` State of the Union . '","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"' `` But I think","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"he could have done it through different channels , ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"she added ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"referring to Trump 's decision","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"to have his personal attorney , Rudy Giuliani , handle it .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"`` He should have probably gone to the DOJ .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"He should have worked through those entities ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"but he chose to go a different route . ''","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"On NBC News ' `` Meet the Press , '' Alexander said","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"he believed","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Trump `` called the president of Ukraine","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"and asked him to become involved in investigating Joe Biden . ''","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"And he said ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"`` at least in part , he delayed the military and other assistance to Ukraine","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"in order to encourage that investigation . ''","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"he should n't have done it .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"it was wrong , ''","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"said Alexander ,","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"who plans to vote for acquittal .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"`` If he was upset about Joe Biden and his son and what they were doing in Ukraine ,","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"he should have called the attorney general","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"and told him that ,","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"and let the attorney general handle it the way","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"they always handle cases","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"that involve public figures , ''","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"said Alexander ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"who is not seeking re-election in November 's election .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"When asked why he thought","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Trump did not go to the DOJ ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Alexander said ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"`` Maybe he did n't know to do it . ''","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"`` I would think","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"he would think twice","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"before he did it again , ''","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"' He shouldn ' t have done it ' :","depth":5},{"id":125,"text":"GOP senator","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"who scolded Trump on Ukraine","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"explains","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"why he backs acquittal","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. , told Fox News on Sunday","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"that `` the day of reckoning is coming for congressional and Senate oversight of Joe Biden . ''","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"`` I 'm going to bring in State Department officials","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"and ask them ,","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"why did n't you do something about the obvious conflict of interests","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Joe Biden had ? ''","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"said Graham ,","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"who previously pledged to have his committee investigate the matter","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"but has not yet scheduled any hearings .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"`` We 're going to get to the bottom of this , ''","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"`` And I can prove beyond any doubt","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"that Joe Biden 's effort in the Ukraine","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"to root out corruption","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"was undercut ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"because he let his son sit on the board of the most corrupt company in the Ukraine ,","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"and we 're not going to give him a pass on that . ''","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"In an interview with Bloomberg News , Ernst said","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"Democrats had lowered the bar for impeachment to the point","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"if Biden were to become president","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"there would be voices","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"calling for his removal","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"because of Hunter Biden 's connection to Burisma .","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"`` I think","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"this door of impeachable whatever has been opened , ''","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"Ernst told Bloomberg .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"`` We can have a situation","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"where","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"if it should ever be President Biden ,","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"that immediately , people , right the day","depth":15},{"id":160,"text":"after he would be elected","depth":15},{"id":161,"text":"would be saying ,","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"'Well , we ' re going to impeach him . ' ''","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"'Is that true ? ' :","depth":6},{"id":164,"text":"Here are questions","depth":6},{"id":165,"text":"senators asked during Trump 's impeachment trial","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":331,"left":167,"right":330,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":330,"left":201,"right":329,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":197,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197